TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

Context("Numeric");

$a = random(2,20,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Suppose that \( f(x) = \sqrt{$a + e^{x} } \).  Find \(f'(2)\).

$BR $BR

\(f'(2)\) = \{ans_rule(30) \}
$BR

EOT

$ans =Compute(".5*($a+exp(2))**(-.5)*exp(2)");

ANS($ans->cmp);

